snippet.textDisplay:
From My Point of View
1: Jungkooks hair
2: Jimin could not stop sitting down it was adorable
3: Just all of their reactions were so funny and cute
4: Taehyung is Dionysus or some other god
5: They spent like a whole minute talking about weather the gate was CG and they spent most of it asking if it was CG or not
6: This music video is now the Lion King remake
7: They all were just waiting for Jungkook to run
8: Jungkook when he watches it the second time is so adorable because he's sad about the bird and explains how it got killed and his obsession with the bird
9: The fact they froze for us and that Jungkook had real thorns on his hands shows how much they love us
10: How much do you wanna bet that the reason they did so many walking scenes was become one of them (most likely Namjoon) was tripping
11: This was literally like a movie and I loved it, I really missed the real sets so I'm really happy about that and I love how they're bringing it back and mixing CG with real sets.
snippet.textOriginal:
From My Point of View
1: Jungkooks hair
2: Jimin could not stop sitting down it was adorable
3: Just all of their reactions were so funny and cute
4: Taehyung is Dionysus or some other god  
5: They spent like a whole minute talking about weather the gate was CG and they spent most of it asking if it was CG or not
6: This music video is now the Lion King remake
7: They all were just waiting for Jungkook to run
8: Jungkook when he watches it the second time is so adorable because he's sad about the bird and explains how it got killed and his obsession with the bird
9: The fact they froze for us and that Jungkook had real thorns on his hands shows how much they love us
10: How much do you wanna bet that the reason they did so many walking scenes was become one of them (most likely Namjoon) was tripping
11: This was literally like a movie and I loved it, I really missed the real sets so I'm really happy about that and I love how they're bringing it back and mixing CG with real sets.
